            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir En Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>In what discourse, then, after this, namely, the Qur'n, will they believe? In other words, they cannot believe in any other of God's Scriptures after having denied this [Qur'n], since it comprises that inimitability (i`jz) which none of the others do. Meccan, consisting of 40 or 41 verses.</p>"
